data.description: Welcome to 3703 Windmill Court! This stunning 4-bedrooms plus bonus home sitting on a half acre lot is now available for sale. With a spacious size of 2653 square feet, this property offers plenty of room for comfortable living.  Step inside and be greeted by an inviting interior that boasts an open floor plan, allowing for seamless flow between rooms. The well-appointed kitchen features modern appliances, ample storage space, and a breakfast bar, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying a quick meal. The bedrooms are generously sized and offer plenty of natural light. The primary bedroom is located on the main level providing convenience and privacy. The 2.5 bathrooms are tastefully designed and equipped with modern fixtures. Situated in a cul-de-sac, this property offers easy access to shopping centers, parks, and major transportation routes. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your dream home!
